short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provide a few buttons for you to nuke some github branches

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you tired of deleting stale branches by hand?

This plugin adds a few buttons on Github web page to delete them all.

You can choose to mass-delete Merged, Closed or All branches on the page.
